064    public static <T extends ApiMethod<T, TResult> & ExpandableTrait<T>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelGetDsl<?, ?, ?, ?>> T get(
065            final T request, final TQuery getDsl) {
066        T updatedRequest = request;
067        for (ExpansionPath<?> expansionPath : getDsl.expansionPaths()) {
068            updatedRequest = (T) updatedRequest.addExpand(expansionPath.toSphereExpand());
069        }
070        return updatedRequest;
071    }

073    public static <T extends ApiMethod<T, TResult> & ExpandableTrait<T>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelGetDsl<?, ?, ?, ?>> T get(
074            final T request, final Supplier<TQuery> createGetDsl, final Function<TQuery, TQuery> getDsl) {
075        MetaModelGetDsl<?, ?, ?, ?> get = getDsl.apply(createGetDsl.get());
076        return get(request, get);
077    }

079    public <T extends ApiMethod<T, TResult> & ExpandableTrait<T>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelGetDsl<?, ?, ?, ?>> T with(
080            final Function<ProjectApiRoot, T> request, final Supplier<TQuery> createGetDsl,
081            final Function<TQuery, TQuery> getDsl) {
082        MetaModelGetDsl<?, ?, ?, ?> get = getDsl.apply(createGetDsl.get());
083        return get(request.apply(apiRoot), get);
084    }
